## CircularButton Button Component

Master button, it renders 6 different buttons in 3 sizes

### PropTypes

| propName | propType | defaultValue | isRequired | options/example |
|----------|----------|--------------|------------|---------|
| onClick     | func   | -      | +          |  |
| style | object   |-           |   -       |  |



### Example

``` js
<CircularButton
  onClick={onClick}
/>
```
